  "content": "Exceptional aroma. Exceptional tea. DISCOVER YOUR RITUAL Exceptional aroma. Exceptional tea. Find Your Moment of Zen At Zen Rojas, we believe every sip is an invitation to slow down, breathe deeply, and reconnect with the present moment. Our premium, organic loose leaf teas are thoughtfully crafted to bring balance, comfort, and calm to your daily routine — from slow mornings to peaceful nights and every mindful m Sleep & Relaxation Calming blends crafted for restful nights. Immune Support Daily wellness support with antioxidant-rich ingredients. Daily Energy Smooth, sustained energy for your daily routine. Digestion Support Comforting blends crafted for balance and ease. Steep Into Something Sacred Thoughtfully crafted loose leaf essentials designed to elevate every calming sip and daily ritual. Tea Infuser Tea Bags Zen Rojas Mug 11oz Your Next Favorite Sip Awaits... Zen Rojas Tea Bag Samplers Zen Rojas Loose Leaf Samplers Organic Black Tea Bodyguard Organic Tea “I have bought it for a family friend and now my cousin(who just gave birth this month). She's been struggling with breastfeeding and the tea gave her a successful breast feeding session today” “Zen Rojas tea has helped me get rid of a sore throat and congestion. I mix the black tea and bodyguard.” “Your sleep tea helped me so much with my insomnia! 10 minutes after drinking it i was out. It tasted and smelled amazing, I will be buying more! Thank you so much” Smells and tastes amazing. Makes a great black tea lemonade.👍 What We Do ”We exist to deliver quality products in a generous and stress free manner that leaves all parties satisfied & zen.” Based in Houston, TX From Our Family to Yours Veteran owned and family operated, Zen Rojas was born from a simple truth: calm is something we create. Through years of",
